          },
          "reviewBody": "I am wordless to see the ANNUAL day celebration by the kids grade 4 to 6.It was Marvels preparation done by your SARVOTTAM team.Very very thank you Dr.PRINCIPAL MAM and all the best team.Once again thank you all members of  S.  I.  S.",
