        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Sarvottam International School - Block N,Delta III"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Sumit Sinha"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-11-20",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My heartfelt gratitude & appreciation for the outstanding organization and execution of this year’s Annual Function, themed “Kautilya – The Legendary Mentor.”\n\nThe theme was inspiring and educational, beautifully showcasing the wisdom and teachings of Kautilya while emphasizing their relevance in today’s world. The performances were exceptionally well-coordinated, and it was evident that the students had put in tremendous effort under the skilled guidance of their teachers.\n\nI was particularly impressed by the engaging choreography, the innovative stage design, and the thoughtful integration of Kautilya's philosophy into the event's various segments. It not only entertained but also left a lasting impression on the audience.\n\nPlease extend my congratulations to the Principal, entire faculty, staff, and students for their hard work and dedication. Events like these highlight the institution’s ability to provide holistic education that blends academic knowledge with cultural and historical understanding.\n\nThank you for fostering such an enriching environment and organizing events that leave a lasting impact on both students and attendees.\n\nWarm regards,\nSumit Sinha\nFather of Siyona Sinha\nClass 6",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
